info.name: OpenIPSL.Examples.Controls.PSSE.ES.ESAC2A
info.description: SMIB model example of GENROU with Excitation System ESAC2A

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.x[1].comment: State of transfer function from controller canonical form

$whenCondition1.comment: eSAC2A.simpleLagLim.state < eSAC2A.simpleLagLim.outMin and eSAC2A.simpleLagLim.K * eSAC2A.imLeadLag.y - eSAC2A.simpleLagLim.state > 0.0

eSAC2A.derivative.T.comment: Time constants (T>0 required; T=0 is ideal derivative block)

eSAC2A.derivative.x_start.comment: Initial or guess value of state

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.a[1].comment: Denominator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 5*s+6 is specified as {5,6})

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.a[2].comment: Denominator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 5*s+6 is specified as {5,6})

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.b[1].comment: Numerator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 2*s+3 is specified as {2,3})

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.b[2].comment: Numerator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 2*s+3 is specified as {2,3})

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.x_start[1].comment: Initial or guess values of states

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.y_start.comment: Initial value of output (derivatives of y are zero up to nx-1-th derivative)

eSAC2A.rectifierCommutationVoltageDrop.g.comment: Gain value multiplied with input signal

eSAC2A.rotatingExciterWithDemagnetizatio.comment: Gain value multiplied with input signal

gENCLS.CoB.comment: Change from system to machine base

generator.PSIppd0.comment: d-axis component of the sub-transient flux linkage

generator.PSIppq0.comment: q-axis component of the sub-transient flux linkage

generator.dsat.comment: To include saturation of during initialization

generator.ii0.comment: Imaginary component of initial armature current (pu, system base)

generator.ir0.comment: Real component of initial armature current (pu, system base)

generator.p0.comment: Initial active power generation (pu, machine base)

generator.q0.comment: Initial reactive power generation (pu, machine base)

generator.vi0.comment: Imaginary component of initial terminal voltage

generator.vr0.comment: Real component of initial terminal voltage

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.initType.comment: Type of initialization (1: no init, 2: steady state, 3: initial state, 4: initial output)

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.na.comment: Size of Denominator of transfer function.

eSAC2A.imLeadLag.TF.nb.comment: Size of Numerator of transfer function.

eSAC2A.limiter1.limitsAtInit.comment: Has no longer an effect and is only kept for backwards compatibility (the implementation uses now the homotopy operator)

eSAC2A.limiter1.strict.comment: = true, if strict limits with noEvent(..)
